title: Readout of President Donald J. Trump’s Call with Prime Minister Theresa May of the United Kingdom – The White House
content:
Statements & Releases			

		Foreign Policy	

Issued on:
June 9, 2017
President Donald J. Trump spoke today with Prime Minister Theresa May of the United Kingdom to offer his warm support regarding the election. President Trump emphasized his commitment to the United States-United Kingdom special relationship and underscored that he looks forward to working with the Prime Minister on shared goals and interests in the years to come.
